{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"84efab61f1","title":"致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c5dfd849ff","index":0,"year":1940,"month":4,"day":25,"articleId":"84efab61f1"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji14","name":"毛泽东全集第14卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji14.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji14":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"69c4de8636","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"84efab61f1"},{"id":"2a4340f96a","type":"paragraph","text":"1940年4月25日）一、时局一方面加重了投降危险，另一方面仍未丧失克服此科危险的可能性。二、国民党的限共与磨擦政策不会改变，但目前还没有与我党立即分裂的意图。三、李品仙部仍在进攻新四军，请令彭昊支队速向苏北前进，第三四四旅速向淮北前进。苏北、淮北、晓东是八路、新四两军最重要的生命线，彼既向我进攻，我自不能坐视。四、蒋邀周去颜迫切。邵力子便苏，似尚有赖苏教急之意。彼方财政经济问题甚严重，军队战斗力大减，人民离心力日增，将的文章并不好做。周去将给以团结抗战之助力","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"84efab61f1"}],"page":{"id":"6f2d14d467","publicationId":"maoquanji14","articleId":"84efab61f1","start":541,"end":541}}}},"__N_SSG":true}